    "partOfSpeech": "contraction",
    "definition": "Informal spoken pronunciation of 'supposed to'.",
    "usageContext": "connected speech",
    "cefrLevel": "B1",
    "examples": [
      {
        "en": "We're supposta meet at five.",
        "hi": "हमें पाँच बजे मिलना है।"
      }
    ],
    "notes": "The 'd' in supposed is elided."
  },
  {
