    "definition": "Informal spoken reduction of 'them'.",
    "usageContext": "connected speech",
    "cefrLevel": "A2",
    "examples": [
      {
        "en": "Give 'em a break.",
        "hi": "उन्हें थोड़ा आराम करने दो।"
      }
