    "partOfSpeech": "verb",
    "definition": "Pronounced as 'kən' (schwa) in positive sentences.",
    "usageContext": "weak form",
    "cefrLevel": "A1",
    "examples": [
      {
        "en": "I can swim.",
        "hi": "मैं तैर सकता हूँ।"
      }
    ],
    "notes": "'Can't' is stressed (rhymes with pant/aunt), while 'can' is reduced."
  },
